version_description:
Performance improvements and bug fixes 
We've also brought the app in line with iOS7 look and feel 

Each new version wipes out old reviews so please help us by leaving a new review. You should be prompted in a few days time! 

We cannot reply to reviews so if you have any feedback for us please email support@pinkfroot.com - we always reply.

We are delighted to introduce this massive update to Ship Finder Free.

Highlights include:

• Incredible performance - view all tracked ships at once! No more clustering!!
• The app is now universal!
• An all new look and feel.
• Augmented Reality (AR) now included.

We hope that you've noticed that our coverage gets better and better too. Thank you to everyone that shares their AIS data with us. Please let us know if you would like to become a part of our network by sharing AIS data.

Thanks as always for all of your feedback and comments too. We do listen - as you have hopefully noticed!!
